Package jwiki.dwrap

Contains data storage formats for jwiki.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Contrib
    Represents a contribution made by a user.
    DataEntry
    Parent template class for contrib/log/revision data.
    ImageInfo
    Container object for a result returned by the imageinfo MediaWiki module.
    LogEntry
    Represents a MediaWiki Log entry
    Revision
    Represents a single revision in the history of a page.

Package jwiki.dwrap Description

Contains data storage formats for jwiki. These are simple objects with public final, immutable fields.
